data.description: Welcome to this stunning single-story home that offers the perfect blend of comfort,  luxury and Pride of Ownership!! * The beauty of the high-end-builder Gehan with a price you can afford with 3-sides Brick!  *An elegant 8 Ft front door opens to a wide entry way with tall ceilings, modern tile, and a Dining Room or perfect space for a Flex Room * Boasting 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms and a Study * This residence is thoughtfully designed with a spacious open floorplan that seamlessly connects the living and kitchen areas * The heart of this home is undoubtedly the kitchen, featuring a magnificent  island that serves as a focal point for culinary enthusiasts and gatherings with gorgeous granite counters and desirable gas cooking * Imagine entertaining guests or preparing meals in this stylish and functional space * The living space extends to the outdoors with a covered porch, providing a delightful area to relax and enjoy the fresh air * Whether it's a morning coffee or an evening sunset, this porch is a versatile extension of your living space * The primary bedroom is a retreat in itself, offering a luxurious super shower for a spa-like experience and a Large Master Closet * The study, adorned with French doors, provides a quiet and elegant space for work or relaxation * Experience the perfect blend of modern design, thoughtful details, and functionality in this one-story haven * Solar Screens, Sprinkler System, Art Niches * The location of this home is perfect for easy access to Randolph AFB, FT Sam Houston, San Antonio, New Braunfels and San Marcos * Riata is a desirable, well maintain community with a community park,  pool,  all in the sought after Schertz-Cibolo-Universal City ISD, walking distance to Sipple Elementary and Schertz School of Science and Technology * Welcome home to a lifestyle of comfort and sophistication!!
